description: Habanero Tacos has been blowing the minds of Minneapolis with their amazingly tasty gourmet Mexican cuisine. Their succulent selection of tacos, burritos, quesadillas, and alambres, are all brimming with your choice of juicy, marinated meats, like al pastor, barbacoa, carne asada, carnitas, and much more. With fresh ingredients and fully robust flavors, it’s no wonder this spicy hot truck is a Minneapolis must-try. So definitely make Habanero Tacos happen whether it’s for your next meal or big event!
name: Habanero Tacos
